  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0d9a\u0db3\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0da2\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A mountain tiger cub died after being caught in a trap",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Officials of the Nuwara Eliya Wildlife Office said that another mountain tiger cub that was caught in a trap died today (25th).",
        "Wildlife officials said that a mountain tiger cub that was caught in a trap set in the tea garden of the Westhall estate under the Nawalapitiya police domain has died in the same place today (25th) morning.",
        "The belly of the tiger cub was caught in a wire trap set in a tea tree by some group to hunt animals roaming in the tea garden.",
        "A group of plantation workers who were working in the tea estate informed the wildlife officials that a mountain tiger had been caught in a trap. When the officials of the Gampola and Nuwara Eliya Wildlife Office went to the place, the mountain tiger was already dead.",
        "Wildlife officials said that after reporting the matter to Nawalapitiya Magistrate's Court regarding the dead mountain tiger, which was about 2 years old, the body of the dead tiger cub will be handed over to Randenigala Veterinary Hospital for post-mortem examination."
      ],
